{"tid":2288542,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"巴絲都入，應該點樣形容呢種女人既心理？","createTime":"2020-11-16T14:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T23:45:54.000Z","uid":227183,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb01369e6e0927d6eebe054fc3cec54c02a78d3","tid":2288542,"uid":227183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"俾女人飛左，女同事黎，佢覺得我唔夠好，咁好啦，<br />\n<br />\n我放左個幾月大假之後番去公司，見番佢本身都無乜野，佢仲會主動say hi，<br />\n<br />\n然後我努力做番好自己，對佢無冷淡，但都無接近，無主動講野，見面打招呼咁囉。<br />\n<br />\n呢排我專注番做野，表現幾好，同事都幾讚我，早幾日都算正常，叫做撞到就有幾句，都幾好笑容，<br />\n<br />\n然後佢今日突然就黑黑地面，<br />\n<br />\n明顯係針對我，公司群組消息佢特登唔回我，(平時佢一定會回的)，做乜會咁？<br />\n<br />\n即係你飛左我，然後我無繼續關心你，你見到我振作番，又唔鍾意？<br />\n<br />\n絲打會唔會理解到？"},{"pid":"eed63d97e4122883454c61c4266f3e9778de3874","tid":2288542,"uid":323900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:07:57.000Z","msg":"佢高估咗自己嘅地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3127aa3601812371213d0b529fd1c5dd6bb4af5a","tid":2288542,"uid":227183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed63d97e4122883454c61c4266f3e9778de3874","tid":2288542,"uid":323900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:07:57.000Z","msg":"佢高估咗自己嘅地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"女人係咪都會咁？"},{"pid":"4b936d2d305a987968643715c7353b53a3577104","tid":2288542,"uid":323900,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3127aa3601812371213d0b529fd1c5dd6bb4af5a","tid":2288542,"uid":227183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed63d97e4122883454c61c4266f3e9778de3874","tid":2288542,"uid":323900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:07:57.000Z","msg":"佢高估咗自己嘅地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"女人係咪都會咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:48:20.000Z","msg":"男女都會嘅，自大又小氣嘅人就會咁樣，分咗都好，起